OL,3,CMan who murdered ex-wife as she put
OL,4,Cflowers on their son's grave jailed
OL,5,Cfor life
OL,7,FA man from Hampshire who armed himself
OL,8,Fwith a 12-inch kitchen knife and laid
OL,9,Fin wait at a cemetery before stabbing
OL,10,Fhis ex-wife to death at the graveside
OL,11,Fof their son, has been jailed for life.
OL,13,FMartin Suter, from Lee-on-the-Solent,
OL,14,Fattacked 71-year-old Ann Blackwood at
OL,15,FCrofton Cemetery in Stubbington, on
OL,16,FJuly 24 2023, which would have been
OL,17,Fthe 36th birthday of their son
OL,18,FChristopher.
OL,20,FChristopher took his own life in 2003
OL,21,Fand the couple had divorced in 2004.
