OL,7,FAt Portsmouth Crown Court, Martin
OL,8,FSuter was told he would serve a
OL,9,Fminimum of 27 years And 230 days in
OL,10,Fprison.
OL,12,FSentencing Suter, who showed no
OL,13,Femotion, at Portsmouth Crown Court,
OL,14,FJudge Michael Bowes KC said: "No
OL,15,Fsentence I can pass can compensate Ann
OL,16,FBlackwood's family and friends for
OL,17,Ftheir devastating loss."
