OL,7,FIn a victim impact statement read to
OL,8,Fcourt, Ms Blackwood's brother John
OL,9,FBlackwood said: "The fact that such
OL,10,Fwickedness can exist and be
OL,11,Fperpetrated by one human being on
OL,12,Fanother is alien to us and totally
OL,13,Fbeyond our comprehension.
OL,15,F"She was an affable, inoffensive
OL,16,Fperson, easy-going, gregarious, with
OL,17,Fmany friends. Her shocking and brutal
OL,18,Fdeath has sorely impacted many people,
OL,19,Fher immediate family and wider circle
OL,20,Fof friends."
